Implements a parser per the following specification:
    https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.11/manual/cmake-language.7.html

You can read the document for the lastest release here:
    https://cmake.org/cmake/help/latest/manual/cmake-language.7.html

1.  Install Bazel (https://bazel.build/)

2.  Configure the runtime.
    ./config

3.  Run the tests:
    bazel test src/...
